messages: Sometimes, we need to be hurt in order to grow. We must lose in order to gain. Sometimes, some lessons are learned best through pain.

I got a lot to say, baby I hope you don’t mind
Hoping you don’t let go
I’m hoping that you’ll hold on
When we make love all night, we really make loveeeeeee ;*
Sometimes, we need to be hurt in order to grow. We must lose in order to gain. Sometimes, some lessons are learned best through pain.
